data.description: BEAUTIFUL FAMILY HOME! This home has 4 bedrooms and 2 remodeled bathrooms and it is ready for you to move right in and relax. It offers plenty of room for the family. Spacious family room in the basement with a gas fireplace. Bonus sunroom or hot tub room off the back of the house. New windows, heated 2 car garage, two storage sheds (8x10 and 12x24) and an underground dog fence. Kitchen appliances included. Call for a showing today!
